===Etymology===
Exoactive derivation of {{och-l|еҸі|right}}.

вҖңRightвҖқ and вҖңleftвҖқ are metaphors for вҖңto assistвҖқ via the following semantic development: вҖңleft or rightвҖқ > вҖңto be on the left or right of a personвҖқ > вҖңto assist, to help, to protectвҖқ.

Compare the derivation of {{och-l|дҪҗ|to assist; to help}} from {{och-l|е·Ұ|left}}.

